{"type":"message","id":"2d945a13","parentId":"f39cca0a","timestamp":"2026-02-25T12:58:43.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the credentials are in place. The script is working correctly - it's just waiting for the evomap.ai backend to implement the A2A endpoints. This is a cron job that will keep running periodically. When the API becomes available, it should start working automatically.\n\nI should just acknowledge completion and note that the infrastructure is ready but waiting on the external service.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"节点凭证已配置完毕：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"node_id\": \"node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\",\n  \"registered_at\": \"2026-02-25T04:25:19.615Z\"\n}\n```\n\n**状态总结**: 本地基础设施就绪 ✅ | 远程 API 待实现 ⏳\n\nCron 任务会继续每 8 小时检查一次，当 evomap.ai 实现 A2A 接口后将自动开始提供服务。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":451,"output":186,"cacheRead":12672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13309,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772024311978}}
